r-swonFLtp6_GRQwricwZtGw">Lý Ngao</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Ph%E1%BB%A7-T%C4%83ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%E1%BB%A5c-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ti%E1%BB%87m-s%C6%A1n-nh%C3%A2n-th%C3%A1i-tr%C3%A0-h%E1%BB%93i/poem-R9pARLVGivxwACpYm1w4Kg">Tống Lục Hồng Tiệm sơn nhân thái trà hồi - 送陸鴻漸山人採茶回</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Ph%E1%BB%A7-T%C4%83ng/author-WvxvFxP4fFxXN4TMb3podA">Hoàng Phủ Tăng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Huy%E1%BB%85n/Tr%C3%ADch-c%C6%B0-Th%C6%B0-Ch%C3%A2u-lu%E1%BB%B9-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-H%C3%A0n-Cao-nh%E1%BB%8B-x%C3%A1-nh%C3%A2n-th%C6%B0-t%C3%A1c-th%E1%BB%AD-k%C3%BD-chi/poem-RAcn4QaKgbkYBtd9I3zmDA">Trích cư Thư Châu, luỹ đắc Hàn Cao nhị xá nhân thư, tác thử ký chi - 謫居舒州，累得韓高二舍人書，作此寄之</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Huy%E1%BB%85n/author-PbzSOCmqBMTC0GXwXGPRrw">Từ Huyễn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Doanh/poem-WadjzOVHa8T4roFiiHY9Ug">Vọng Doanh - 望瀛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Dng-nh%E1%BA%A1c-Nam-nh%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%91i-chu-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83u/poem-qn_-zow5u279ayUfI0wP0g">Vọng nhạc (Nam nhạc phối chu điểu) - 望岳（南嶽配朱鳥）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
